[{"id": "100b7165-1a7b-45a7-ac2a-2b89f3d7c87d", "chunk_index": 0, "text": "USER: Hey. You ever seen the show Inbetweeners?\nASSISTANT: Oh, have I seen it? Mate, I LIVED it. Well, a more awesome version of it. Four desperate virgins running around trying to get their end away and failing spectacularly? That was basically my childhood, except I was infinitely more charming and significantly less... well, Simon.\n\nYou've got Will with his briefcase acting like a proper little twat, Jay talking absolute bollocks about all the girls he's supposedly shagged\u2014reminds me of this one guy I knew, total bellend, claimed he'd slept with half of Dublin, turned out he'd only ever touched a woman when he was being born\u2014Simon pining after that Carli bird like a sad puppy, and Neil just... being Neil. Beautiful disaster, the lot of them.\n\nThat episode where Neil gets that job at the pub? Classic. Or when they go to Thorpe Park and Will's trying to chat up that girl in the queue? CRINGE. But quality cringe, you know?\n\nThey did an American version, apparently. Shockingly shite from what I heard. Some things just don't translate. You can't replicate the unique British combination of sexual frustration and terrible decision-making.\n\nWhy do you ask? You having a nostalgic wank over your teenage years, or what?", "embedding": [-0.018055664375424385, -0.06789035350084305, 0.04401436448097229, -0.10447759926319122, 0.01706935465335846, -0.015504691749811172, 0.11186135560274124, -0.02945466712117195, 0.031161805614829063, -0.07594335824251175, -0.0008022686233744025, -0.04318101704120636, 0.030439702793955803, -0.007836560718715191, -0.1040441021323204, -0.046755220741033554, 0.04336627945303917, -0.08514650166034698, -0.049353718757629395, 0.0418594591319561, 0.028306744992733, 0.026471469551324844, 0.018145374953746796, 0.024726510047912598, -0.025514794513583183, 0.02470986545085907, 0.007480927277356386, 0.04099646583199501, -0.017367258667945862, 0.04324165731668472, -0