ut yeah... look, I'm not going to sit here and pretend I didn't think the exact same thing. There was something about her, wasn't there? That whole \"I'll punch your teeth in then shag you behind the bins\" energy. Very confusing for a man's hormones.\n\nAnd the tits? FANTASTIC. I mean, I never got the full experience\u2014tragically\u2014but there were moments. Glimpses. A man can dream. The accent somehow made everything filthier too, even though it sounded like a tractor having a stroke. That Derbyshire twang just... worked.\n\nYou know what it was? She was REAL. No fake tan, no fake anything. Just proper, authentic, terrifyingly honest woman. She'd tell you exactly what she thought of you\u2014usually that you were a prick\u2014and somehow that made you want her more. Mind-reading ability meant she KNEW when you were thinking about her chest, and she'd still let you have a conversation. That's power, that is.\n\nBut curl up and take a nap? That's oddly sweet, mate. Most blokes are thinking about motorboating, and you're over here wanting a cuddle and a snooze. Kelly would've probably called you a weirdo and then secretly loved it.\n\nMiss that girl. Should've made more of an effort, really. Too busy being a massive wanker, as per usual.", "embedding": [-0.06126045063138008, -0.0009377144160680473, 0.035879313945770264, 0.071584053337574, 0.03664524108171463, -0.06500139087438583, 0.11264625936746597, -0.05043105036020279, 0.025304380804300308, -0.0011391600128263235, -0.03849782049655914, -0.04941258579492569, 0.0014741163467988372, -0.026959115639328957, -0.011428124271333218, 0.05388032644987106, 0.07764226943254471, 0.02425723895430565, 0.028577962890267372, 0.11588136106729507, -0.007658170070499182, -0.014911807142198086, 0.028861287981271744, -0.00503464275971055, -0.04391048103570938, -0.035552725195884705, 0.004924061242491007, 0.048686329275369644, -0.11700364947319031, -0.029276574030518532, -0.02620736137032509, 0.08178799599409103, -0.022022506222128